Date: Sat, 27 Jun 2026 00:31:39 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add Journaling Coach and Self-Guided Practices agent modes

Make all four companion modes use distinct system prompts. Adds
journalingSystemPrompt + practicesSystemPrompt and a systemPromptForMode
dispatcher; chat route routes each session.mode to its prompt; companion
page exposes the two new mode cards.
